{
  "stem": "21582.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- well, and then we went to Czestochowa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In Czestochowa, essentially, we did the same thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] hunger, tremendous hunger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "To this day, if we go to a restaurant I'll always, always remark, mmm, the bread is so wonderful.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the potatoes are so wonderful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't think-- I cannot tell you, even to this day, the-- the taste of a crumb of bread dissolving in my mouth surpasses the most-- most exquisite food, and potatoes.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then-- I guess we can-- this is where we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And maybe I should proceed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] shortly before we were liberated-- but we had absolutely no-- no knowledge what was happening in the world and whether the Germans were winning or whether the Germans were losing.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, we always calculated, and speculated that, well, if they move us from this camp to that camp, what does it mean?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Does it mean they're moving us closer to the Allies, further from the Allies?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Does it mean that they are getting a licking?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Is there hope?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, our biggest, biggest dream was to be-- the most-- most-- most welcome wish, would be to be bombed by-- by-- by-- by the Allies.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the biggest wish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to really dream about that and talk about that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every time we heard an airplane, oh, let them just send a few bombs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Let them just-- let them just, you know, bomb it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had no knowledge what-- what was going on outside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At one point, I think that the Germans told us that they are going to save us, from-- which, you know, it just sounded so crazy.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we didn't know what to make of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
